data.description: Perfect painted brick farmhouse built in 1940 and updated in 2023 with things that really matter--vapor barrier and termite bond, new electrical panel, new insulation, new ceiling in the kitchen, new flooring and new sheetrock in several rooms. Located in the top ranked Heard County school system just 20 miles from downtown Newnan. 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms with a large family area and a charming country kitchen. A little over 3 acres! The large carport and paved driveway can accommodate multiple cars or trucks and the two porches are perfect for peaceful country nights. The lot also features an axillary building that is perfect for equipment or a workshop.
